column1: # This file contains our own FMI parameter definitions for testing purposes. In practice,
# we give fmi-id and fmi-name for newbase parameters (fmi-id = 1000000000 + newbase-id).
# Notice that we have also defined for testing purposes so that grib-id = 1000000000 + newbase-id.
# Now grib-id is also same as the fmi-id and the fmi-name is the same as the newbase-name.
